milestones.description: Jonty Rhodes and Cullinan's 92-run partnership is SA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 88 between Wessels and Hansie Cronje
Saleem Malik and Aaqib Javed's 81-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 64 between Tahir Naqqash and Ramiz Raja
Andrew Hudson has scored 17 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SA breaking Hansie Cronje's record
McMillan has broken the record for most catches (34) in ODIs for SA, going past Hansie Cronje's 32
